<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>You can't overwrite the headers sent by apache.</p>

<p>h3. Steps to reproduce</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$this-&gt;getResponse()-&gt;setHeader('Cache-Control', 'must-revalidate', true);
</code></pre>

<p>h3. Expected result
...
Cache-Control: must-revalidate
...</p>

<p>h3. Actual result
Cache-Control: no-store, no-cache, must-revalidate, post-check=0, pre-check=0, <em>must-revalidate</em></p>

